@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(0.53))
    v2 = (0.95 + (wp.exp(tmp + 0.00) + v2))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.81)) * wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = ((0.36 * v0) * ((tmp + 0.41 * v1 + 0.64) / (v0 + 0.41 - v2 + 0.44)))
    v2 = (((v1 + 0.59 + tmp + 0.69) * (v2 + 0.06 / v2 + 0.15)) * (tmp - wp.abs(v2 + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
